          <div className="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <div className="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16">
              <div className="reveal-clip flex-1 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://assets.evolusite.fr/ik-seo/3/img_4750_6EbPVDf59/img_4750_6EbPVDf59.jpg"
                  alt="Vignes Famille Cognard en Agriculture Biologique"
                  className="w-full h-80 md:h-[450px] object-cover" />
              </div>
              <div className="flex-1 space-y-6">
                <div className="reveal-up flex items-center gap-3">
                  <Leaf className="w-5 h-5" style={{ color: '#7aab2e' }} />
                  <span className="text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase" style={{ fontFamily: F.ui, color: '#7aab2e' }}>Agriculture Biologique</span>
                </div>
                <VariableText
                  as="h2"
                  className="reveal-up text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[1.05]"
                  style={{ fontFamily: F.display }}
                  weightStart={300}
                  weightEnd={500}
                  spacingStart={0.02}
                  spacingEnd={-0.02}
                  scaleStart={1}
                  scaleEnd={1.02}
                  breathe={true}
                  breatheDuration={4}
                >
                  La vigne vivante<br /><em style={{ color: '#a8c73a' }}>sans compromis</em>
                </VariableText>
                <p className="reveal-up text-lg leading-[1.8]" data-delay="0.15" style={{ color: 'rgba(26,10,10,0.6)' }}>
                  En 2016, toute chimie disparaît des vignes. En 2017, la conversion bio commence.
                  En 2020, la certification Agriculture Biologique est obtenue. Nos 15 hectares
                  vivent selon les rythmes de la nature — taille raisonnée, mulching de sarments,
